    • Order

      public Order​(int type, int ink, int paper, int glue, int cover, int id, int quantity, String date_created, String date_finished, int dept, int cid)
      Parameters:
      type - the predefined type of book
      ink - the ink needed to craft 10 books
      paper - the paper needed to craft 10 books
      glue - the glue needed to craft 10 books
      cover - the cover units needed to craft 10 books
      id - the id of the order
      quantity - the quantity of the book type
      date_created - the date in which the order was created
      date_finished - the date in which the order was finished, 2021-10-21 if not finished
      dept - the dept to that the order is assigned
      cid - the id of the customer that ordered
